Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you pick which I'm gonna gouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your head? Or your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin! Please kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're with that lizard-bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop dead, Worms!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.01,0:00:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You...! Could you be the doctor from Hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Shin?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujita...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe this guy my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So today's just going to be like this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Chota...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, please have some tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How does the poison tea taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you being so mean to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As En's partner you'll always be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't know anything about En or the family!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of that, I called you here today to watch this movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:03:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,En produced it, wrote the screenplay and starred in the lead role himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,An autobiographical, non-fiction movie depicting the first half of his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Boss - Death Mushrooms"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,450)}Chapter One: Hell
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When I opened my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surrounded by mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently even my parents had turned into mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived by eating the mushrooms around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a man I didn't recognize came to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He was probably a burglar...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When he found a baby there, he went and took me somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He sold me to a filthy abolished factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be your home from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,After that was pure hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The people controlling that abolished factory were low class sorcerers who could barely use any magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They snatched away mid and top class sorcerers from here and there and tied them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They forced them to put out smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And sold that for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time there were a lot of people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,750)}Nine years later
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked there for nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And when my smoke dried up, they threw me in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, mistaking me for a corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A devil sent me to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But even though I was cast down to hell, I didn't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of my hatred for those people, my life refused to burn in the flames of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,750)}Two years later
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chidaruma, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A sorcerer living in hell...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Chidaruma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They named me En.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,750)}Half a year later
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I returned to that abolished factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Put out more smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I destroyed that factory...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And made the sorcerers who were working there my allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tenjin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let us thank you somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm En.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to rid this world of people like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is how the family began.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of my allies kept increasing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And those scumbags started to fear me and gradually disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,450)}Chapter Two: The Enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, more than twenty years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,En, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been some weird murders lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! The guy kills 'em and only takes the head with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems like he's aiming only for skilled sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! We should fuck him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like a job for us! Right, senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the guy some pervert or what? Taking the heads with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They got us! They got three of our guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I s-saw him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who did it had cross-marks on his eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross-marked eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We did what we could, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cross-eye kept killing our men one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use myself as bait and lure that bastard out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rush it, Noi. That's how they all got killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenjin is tracking his hideout down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay calm until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me. Tenjin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it, En.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in Mastema, in an apartment complex called Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Send Shin and Noi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down, Noi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Another headless body...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be Tenjin...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenjin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, you're alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, I was heading to Mastema by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin and Noi should definitely be able to deal with that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had been through so many bloodbaths that I just had a hunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And an indescribable feeling of unease was building up in my chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,These masks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it. Gotta be Shin and Noi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They told me the story afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That time they both felt something they had never felt before from that Cross-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A really strange feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Noi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So we...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Both die here... It's like fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Noi with you and get out of here with this broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,En...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw that man, I felt it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And unless I defeated him here, I wouldn't have a future!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to, I was surrounded by countless mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no sign of anyone near me, the air felt cold to my skin and everything was quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He had broken my mask with his knife and left a shallow wound on my throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My smoke had swallowed the town of Mastema and turned everything into mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the truth behind the "Death Shroom Incident".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was certain I had turned that Cross-eye into a mushroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A headless man, disappearing through a door...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a really interesting movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand the history of the family better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Although according to Noi, the movie is dramatized quite a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great movie no matter how many times I watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,En! When did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- The movie is still unfinished and I haven't released it to the general public yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The movie is still unfinished and I haven't released it to the general public yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want to finish it with the fact that I destroyed the Cross-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I have been searching for a sorcerer who can control time is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To be able to go back to that day, six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the man with the cross-marked eyes die, or did he live?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know the whole truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cross-marked eyes... Man without a head...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sounds similar to that time when I first met Caiman...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:02.48,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,829)}"See You At The Food Stall"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Caiman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the cape?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikaido...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my fault you got caught by that En guy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's why I'll make sure to save you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tanba's restaurant", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna make a fortune today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to bring three people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is our part-tim-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tanba's wife! We just got married three days ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My congratulations...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And your name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Pieman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman, yet called Pie..."man"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are your passes. Keep them where they can be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an entire town inside this guy's castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This place ain't half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that wagon...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the way. Move it, monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now! Who are you calling a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my wagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanba...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She worked for us before you, Pieman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I opened my own shop. A {\i1}pie{\i0} shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you steal Tanba's recipe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuyama... Don't say something so disgraceful about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I just referenced it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Tanba's new wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,New wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She used to be really into president Tanba...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But he completely ignored her and she quit the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My! Such a cold story!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's cold about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huge...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she really a woman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway! From now on you'll be our business rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think you'll be able to sell much when you're right next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you haven't heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who gets more sales during lunch time tomorrow gets to put their shop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case it'd be the same to just hand me the victory right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are full of confidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what if I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case I'll close my shop and start working for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a promise then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't get careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron! You know she can't cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be alright to do a little scouting inside the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Work comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Our ingredients should've arrived at the back entrance of the southern building!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a bossy husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Squee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, Jonson!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:12:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to save Nikaido, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, you'd better return to Hole right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful for what you did in the past, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are the lizard-man's friends so that makes us enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that certainly seems to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... I'll turn a blind eye this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to stop associating with the lizard-man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me to keep my nose out of unnecessary business...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks to me sticking my nose in some unnecessary business ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are both alive today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Vaux?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, yeah, I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is helping people your hobby or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... I'm only interested in research!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You never change...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Caiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the En family newsletter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? "The Boss's five favorite mushrooms..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is Nikaido in the news?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she forcibly taken into this castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Caiman? Caiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Everything's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Caiman's going to be alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To be like this over a woman, how ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Tanba!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice to see you being so affectionate with your wife today as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really knew it already...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Nikaido is a sorcerer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just didn't want to admit it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikaido was lying to me about being a human...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if I even need to save her anymore...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, this is where she really belongs...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Might be better to just quietly leave this castle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, that's it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And think this carefully through by myself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you go to the square at lunch time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The two shops there will compete in a pie showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We will also have executives from the family participating as special judges!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So why don't you take part in this contest as a customer as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go, Nikaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikaido...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is that the woman you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear! We need to beat that Asuka woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We should go back to the wagon and get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's doing better than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess she didn't need me to come and save her after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,President! We have thirty pies ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! There's gonna be a line right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,President! The customers are here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, bring 'em on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me one of Asuka's special apple pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still plenty to go around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only noon but it looks like we already have our winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and lemme eat some!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious apple pies, here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, that sure is a nice, sweet scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy Asuka's pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm buying some.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the apple pies...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You want the sweet one instead of the meat, senpai? That's unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And for En to get something other than mushrooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me some buns too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, dear... What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go check it out real quick...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The pies are heart-shaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's so-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not worth waiting in line for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Asuka just lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Such a fine woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eat more of her pies...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be really happy if we buy a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to compete with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get the meat pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so good about that bitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That Fukuyama sure is taking his time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me work here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you buy some more pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now. That's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Asuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll soon need the next batch of pies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you can't let anyone in here, understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.72,Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\pos(673.6,688.8)}Frozen pies - Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.72,Handwriting 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(665.6,954.4)}Microwave for 3 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I need more pies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka's magic summons a monster called "Angel"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And it can make any man fall for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably using that smoke to lure the men in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And casting the magic on the pies by feeding them to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So why are you alright, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She used her magic too much on me so I developed an immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Her magic's not affecting you either?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, I'm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us some pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:18:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido's alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I leave the shop now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like there's gonna be a big difference whether you're here or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really help that much at the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it. I didn't even pay you your salary yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Caiman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come back for my paycheck someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, if I still have a shop then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow day, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Two meat pies, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the judges!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming right up, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're freshly baked, so eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It has venison that was soaked in red wine with vegetables for a whole day, minced veal and thinly diced foie gras!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme another! No, gimme ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Asuka... You've been using your magic for too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel... More pies...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What were we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting a heartburn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So this means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be out of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Fifteen minutes left! We won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, president!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I have one of your pies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try both so that I make a fair decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. En!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:21:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you only eat mushrooms so I specifically prepared this chanterelle pie for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Chanterelles!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the winner, Tanba.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Work hard with your business from now on as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So you had a pie like that prepared, president!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Tanba!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I gotta get away for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If En finds out I cast my magic on him he'll kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Caiman, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? We're getting away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I... want to be near En.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're not coming, I'll drag you with me by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What we learned from the eleventh curse:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,1. En was a cute little kid... NOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,2. En's mansion is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.21,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,3. Tanba's pies are super good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you will learn from the twelfth curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That is still a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.78,0:23:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,DOROHEDORO

